name: join
description: Allows you to enter the game if you’re spectating.

name: afk
description: Allows you to enter spectate after a couple of seconds. Each time is different when you use it. Max is 19 seconds.

name: drop
description: Whatever item you’re holding in your hands, you drop it.

name: nextrank
description: Shows how many more points you need for the next rank.

name: points
description: Shows the current amount of points that you have.

name: maptop
description: Shows the current map’s best and worst player.

name: top20
description: Shows the top 20 players in the server.

name: top15
description: Shows the top 15 players in the server.

name: top10
description: Shows the top 10 players in the server.

name: next
description: Shows the next map along with the amount of times the current map has been failed.

name: mut
description: Brings up a menu of the current players and allows you to mute someone

name: showpoints
description: Shows your rank and your points to everyone.

name: info
description: Shows you another player’s rank, health, etc.
